text: Ismael Ankobo (born October 13, 1997 in Ouenzé) is a Congolese football player who is currently plays for CARA. He was part of the Congo squad that is participated in the qualification of the 2018 World Cup. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Republic of the Congo footballers Category:Republic of the Congo international footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:AS Kondzo players Category:Ittihad Tanger players Category:AS FAR (football) players Category:CARA Brazzaville players Category:Botola players Category:Republic of the Congo expatriate footballers Category:Republic of the Congo expatriate sportspeople in Morocco Category:Expatriate footballers in Morocco Category:Sportspeople from Brazzaville
